<section style="margin: 10px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: FZShuSong-Z01; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2857em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">“夫辩者，将以明是非之分，审治乱之纪，明同异之处，察名实之理，处利害，决嫌疑”。为了丰富校园文化生活，陶冶学生情操，提高口才艺术修养，培养同学们的语言思辨能力和团队协作能力与意识。在初冬之际，经济管理学院学生会积极组织同学们参加辩论赛。11月29日晚上6时，经济管理学院辩论赛预赛正式拉开帷幕。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2857em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705117514630075016.jpg" title="1705117514630075016.jpg" alt="c6fd1d31bb0e62e33e2b08cb5a4c113e.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: FZShuSong-Z01; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2857em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2.2857em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一时强弱在于力，万古胜负在于理，“辩论”作为一种文化，是大学生活中不可缺少的一部分，“思辨”的精神亦是同学们不可缺少的特质。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: FZShuSong-Z01; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.2857em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2.2857em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在主持人介绍本场辩论赛的规则和评分细则后，辩论赛正式拉开序幕。各位辩手在场上引经据典，唇枪舌剑。辩论激起了经管学子思想的碰撞与创新的火花。辩手们通过辩论表达个人见解，摆脱旧有观念束缚，代表着青年学子们从未停止思考，从未怯于表达。析世事、寻真理，求公正、明人心。时代的问题亟需作答，而辩论为其纵深剖析。它让我们不仅关注到近处的是非，也了解到远方的诉泣。辩论广阔的格局与视野同时也让我们每一个血气奔涌的青年人更加具有为国家担当作为的信心和勇气。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2857em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-flow: row nowrap;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: auto; flex: 0 0 0%; height: auto; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;"></section></section></section><p><br/></p>